.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-FEE-REVENUE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-fee-revenue \- show total routing fee revenue
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-fee-revenue
.RB [ --since
.IR unix_timestamp ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the count and total fees from settled forwards.
Use
.B --since
to restrict to a time window.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"count":N, "total_fee_msat":N, "total_fee_sat":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-forwarding-stats (1),
.BR lightning-channel-fee-earned (1)
